Package com.osoc6.OSOC6.repository

package com.osoc6.OSOC6.repository
This package contains all repository's used for the API. A repository is an interface implemented by Spring. A repository is our way to the database. Using the Spring Rest data dependency a repository also creates endpoints and no service and controllers are needed.
